    "headline": "Kimberly-Clark Announces Post-Closing Organizational Structure and Identifies Key Leadership",
    "summary": "Kimberly‑Clark Corporation (NASDAQ: KMB) today announced the organizational structure and key leadership that will become effective upon completion of its pending acquisition of Kenvue Inc. (NYSE: KVUE). The organizational structure, roles, and responsibilities reflect the fast-and-lean, balanced matrix approach that has built strong operating momentum at Kimberly-Clark since implementing its Powering Care strategy two years ago.",
